0.name: 1Lost note
0.text:
It has been a strange past few days.
Of course that is the usual around here but some things appear off.
Stranger than usual.

We noticed that the water filters have been burnt through.
There was a substantial buildup in acidir material in the pipelines.
Luckilly no leakages but it is strange how none of us noticed the.. acidic taste in the water supply.
We have been drinking this for days.

1.name: 2Lost note
1.text:
Things are getting weirder.
It has only been slightly over a week since the renowned Crescent of Curses arrived on our doorstep.

I fear unlike the other artefacts we collected, this one appears to radiate some sort of aura which messes with the brain.

At least the filter has been replaced.
Unfortunately it was only after one of us took a warm bath and melted overnight.

We need to get rid of that thing.

2.name: 3Lost note
2.text:
We should never have accepted that Crescent of Curses.
Some of us have gone mad!

This morning we discovered three more skeletons at the bottom of the lakes.
I fear out of sheer madness they went for an acidic swim.

I too have experienced some strange things.
Sometimes when I look down a hallway, it starts expanding.
Like there are more than a million other ways to go.

It shows things that nobody can see.

3.text:
